2026-05-14T04:09:19.3603892Z 13    <!--
2026-05-14T04:09:19.3604553Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-14T04:09:19.3605518Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-14T04:09:19.3606888Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-14T04:09:19.3607914Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-14T04:09:19.3608971Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-14T04:09:19.3610000Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-14T04:09:19.3611057Z 20    -->
2026-05-14T04:09:19.3611837Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
